Class IngredientStack

cs.eng1.piazzapanic.stations.IngredientStack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,FixedStack<Ingredient>>
public class IngredientStack extends HashMap<String,FixedStack<Ingredient>>
An ingredient stack acts like a collection of FixedStack<Ingredient>, where there can be many ingredients of different types, but only a specified maximum amount of ingredient per type. This allows RecipeStation to create a Recipe out of Ingredients that are out of order.
Author:
Andrey Samoilov
